Moshe Ndiki to co-host the the 11th annual Feather Awards on 17 October. JOHANNESBURG – This year marks the 11th annual Feather Awards on 17 October. Rami Chuene & Moshe Ndiki to host the prestigious awards. The nominees of the 2019 Feather Awards were announced on Thursday at Constitution Hill. See the full list of nominees: Best Styled Individual •    Manthe Ribane
